{"sn24.44:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 24.44 ","sn24.44:0.2":"2. Dutiyagamanavagga ","sn24.44:0.3":"Adukkhamasukhisutta ","sn24.44:1.1":"“Adukkhamasukhi atta hoti arogo param marana”ti? ","sn24.44:1.2":"“Bhagavammulaka no, bhante, dhamma …pe… ","sn24.44:2.1":"“Rupe kho, bhikkhave, sati, rupam upadaya, rupam abhinivissa evam ditthi uppajjati: ","sn24.44:2.2":"‘adukkhamasukhi atta hoti arogo param marana’ti. ","sn24.44:2.3":"Vedanaya sati … ","sn24.44:2.4":"sannaya sati … ","sn24.44:2.5":"sankharesu sati … ","sn24.44:2.6":"vinnane sati, vinnanam upadaya, vinnanam abhinivissa evam ditthi uppajjati: ","sn24.44:2.7":"‘adukkhamasukhi atta hoti arogo param marana’ti. ","sn24.44:3.1":"Tam kim mannatha, bhikkhave, rupam niccam va aniccam va”ti? ","sn24.44:3.2":"“Aniccam, bhante” …pe… ","sn24.44:3.3":"viparinamadhammam, api nu tam anupadaya evam ditthi uppajjeyya: ","sn24.44:3.4":"‘adukkhamasukhi atta hoti arogo param marana’”ti? ","sn24.44:3.5":"“No hetam, bhante”. ","sn24.44:3.6":"“Iti kho, bhikkhave, dukkhe sati, dukkham upadaya, dukkham abhinivissa evam ditthi uppajjati: ","sn24.44:3.7":"‘adukkhamasukhi atta hoti arogo param marana’”ti. ","sn24.44:3.8":"“Vedana … ","sn24.44:3.9":"sanna … ","sn24.44:3.10":"sankhara … ","sn24.44:3.11":"vinnanam niccam va aniccam va”ti? ","sn24.44:3.12":"“Aniccam, bhante” …pe… ","sn24.44:3.13":"viparinamadhammam, api nu tam anupadaya evam ditthi uppajjeyya: ","sn24.44:3.14":"‘adukkhamasukhi atta hoti arogo param marana’”ti? ","sn24.44:3.15":"“No hetam, bhante”. ","sn24.44:3.16":"“Iti kho, bhikkhave, dukkhe sati, dukkham upadaya, dukkham abhinivissa evam ditthi uppajjati: ","sn24.44:3.17":"‘adukkhamasukhi atta hoti arogo param marana’”ti. ","sn24.44:3.18":"Chabbisatimam. ","sn24.44:3.19":"Dutiyapeyyalo. ","sn24.44:4.0":"Tassuddanam ","sn24.44:4.1":"Vatam etam mama so, ","sn24.44:4.2":"atta no ca me siya; ","sn24.44:4.3":"Natthi karoto hetu ca, ","sn24.44:4.4":"mahaditthena atthamam. ","sn24.44:5.1":"Sassato asassato ceva, ","sn24.44:5.2":"antanantava ca vuccati; ","sn24.44:5.3":"Tam jivam annam jivanca, ","sn24.44:5.4":"tathagatena cattaro. ","sn24.44:6.1":"Rupi atta hoti arupi ca atta hoti, ","sn24.44:6.2":"Rupi ca arupi ca atta hoti; ","sn24.44:6.3":"Neva rupi narupi atta hoti, ","sn24.44:6.4":"Ekantasukhi atta hoti. ","sn24.44:7.1":"Ekantadukkhi atta hoti, ","sn24.44:7.2":"Sukhadukkhi atta hoti; ","sn24.44:7.3":"Adukkhamasukhi atta hoti, ","sn24.44:7.4":"Arogo param maranati; ","sn24.44:7.5":"Ime chabbisati sutta, ","sn24.44:7.6":"Dutiyavarena desita. "}